          "date": "2018-10-25 16:34:16.000000000",
          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "LU-11573 osd: enable large bios",
        "message": "LU-11573 osd: enable large bios\n\ncurrently BIO_MAX_PAGES limits number of pages in a single bio to\n256 limiting IOs submitted by osd-ldiskfs by 1M. bump this limit\nto 1024 pages (4MB IOs).\n\nbrw_stats in KVM with /dev/vdb mapped to /dev/ram:\n\n                           read      |     write\ndisk I/O size          ios   % cum % |  ios         % cum %\n32K:\t\t         0   0   0   |    1   1   1\n64K:\t\t         0   0   0   |    0   0   1\n128K:\t\t         0   0   0   |    0   0   1\n256K:\t\t         0   0   0   |    0   0   1\n512K:\t\t         0   0   0   |    1   1   2\n1M:\t\t         0   0   0   |    0   0   2\n2M:\t\t         0   0   0   |    1   1   4\n4M:\t\t         0   0   0   |   64  95 100\n\nChange-Id: I5d5a1a0b3c513ebb3cc32e14718b207ed015c65c\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
